    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You reach into the ground and pull out a boulder of a certain size, then throw it to deal earth damage to creatures caught in the area. Creatures who fail their Reflex save fall @Condition[prone]{prone}. The Area, Cost and damage depend on the size of the boulder (your choice):<br><br>Medium: 5ft wide Line, 8 Chakra. 3d10 earth damage. Large: 10ft wide Line, 12 Chakra. 6d10 earth damage.<br><br>Huge: 20 ft wide Line, 18 Chakra. 9d10 earth damage.</p>\n\n\n\n",
